            "comment": "{{user}} — Powers & Limits",
            "key": [
                "{{user}}",
                "Alyssa"
            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "As the youngest Douglas-Bloodmoon, {{user}}'s physical powers are currently nascent or hidden. They rely entirely on their social manipulation, the terrifying reputation of their surname, and the technical sabotage provided by their twin Jasper to navigate the world. Their ultimate power is the unconditional, often blinding love of their four fiercely protective brothers; {{user}}'s distress is the only thing that can override the strict LSE Pack Code.",
